               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Gadla Libānos “Vita of Libānos” (fols. 4ra-15va)&#xD;
II) Taʾāmra Libānos “Miracles of Libānos”: 35 miracles (fols. 15va–59vb)&#xD;
III) Mälkәʾa Libānos “Image of Libānos”: 31 strophes (fols. 60ra–63rb)&#xD;
&#xD;
Additiones 1-3.</summary>
